cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.SI, cs.DL 

This paper is about an unsupervised method for keyword extraction from text, which falls under the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), and machine learning (cs.LG). The method uses network analysis and graph-based centrality approaches, which are also relevant to social network analysis (cs.SI) and deep learning (cs.DL).
